data.description: Great opportunity to own this ranch home located in NE Des Moines. A great location for someone looking for a nice neighborhood with all the nearby amenities Altoona and Des Moines has to offer.  Great buy on this updated home! This 3 bedroom (4th bedroom non-conforming) ranch offers beautiful hardwood flooring throughout, newly updated kitchen including granite countertops. Basement is partially finished with the 4th potential bedroom, a shower and a large storage area! Property has a new deck/patio new roof on shed (2020) and newer roof (2019) along with beautiful landscaping!! Don't miss out on this one! All information obtained from Seller and public records.
